    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a time capsule of automotive elegance. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a symphony of hand-stitched leather and polished wood that hums with the legacy of a thousand sunset drives. Every curve of its pristine silhouette reflects a life of pampered luxury, preserved so perfectly it feels as though it rolled off the showroom floor yesterday. To drive it is to command a masterpiece of engineering, where the engine\u2019s purr is a whisper of untold stories and the road ahead feels like a canvas waiting for your signature. This is your invitation to own a legend, a rare survivor that demands to be cherished.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
